{"tid":1617433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係應該搞国企同福建幫先，而唔係搞藍色港商？！","createTime":"2019-10-03T19:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:24:10.000Z","uid":303932,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3acfcdad5eac913a755df9ced9967c91a9d02d0","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"最近大家搞到美心營運既Starbucks雞毛鴨血，非常成功，上埋彭博。但大家有無諗過一個問題：<br />\n搞死左Starbucks咪益晒Pacific Coffee?<br />\n咁Pacific Coffee係邊個架？<span style=\"color: red;\">華潤</span>囉！<br />\n屌你！国企來既？！仲要唔係特許經營！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%2592%2596%25E5%2595%25A1&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e33a84d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有香港麥當勞2017年已經賣左盤，俾邊個？<span style=\"color: red;\">中信</span>囉！屌你！又係国企來既？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=1b5d00fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%2F&h=7ed00967\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC/</a><br />\n<br />\n學老毛統戰術諗，&ldquo;聯合次要敵人，打倒主要敵人&rdquo;！<br />\n要搞係唔係要搞左<span style=\"color: red;\">国企</span>先呢？仲有仆街福建幫！哩D係<span style=\"color: red;\">主要敵人</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（仲有邊D係國企，要搵晒出來抵制！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n藍色港商只係<span style=\"color: red;\">次要敵人</span>，受到教訓至少唔會再亂出聲（咁當然仲要沖出來柒我都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），更應拉攏！<br />\n<br />\n最後一句：各位手足真係唔好打爛Starbucks同麥當勞，始終係美帝全球文化象徵，要畀兩分薄面美帝，人地咁幫手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"d22847a3dd1b7fb0adbca8da1686df9fb19dbd9e","tid":1617433,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"52560bb2a130996318cc2cd04674ea98708ab785","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"真係唔好硬膠膠益左Pacific Coffee！推！"},{"pid":"c3f34a7884d56ac2cc0162753b91ae337bbcd8f6","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:30:06.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"4a94b7c2334b8b6d7e6b8140c79173662f1ad384","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:47:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"cfb5fac55909d7f79af4b6c8a10bd4c5c271c489","tid":1617433,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:48:46.000Z","msg":"係羅<br />\n幾時搞老麥？"},{"pid":"980af7b6eacb0caf7c380080bedf8d4ab811d23b","tid":1617433,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:49:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ce52b479348a53570618165ee8a91f4dd7fb1c32","tid":1617433,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33eefbbf85c83ecab9ad63b39b2e107588f760c0","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T20:06:18.000Z","msg":"瞓醒再自推"},{"pid":"efc586c3bdfb6c8e95739858478b1edca7a8f2c8","tid":1617433,"uid":76848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52560bb2a130996318cc2cd04674ea98708ab785","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"真係唔好硬膠膠益左Pacific Coffee！推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T20:29:36.000Z","msg":"巴打你個睇法好好<br />\n但父女同共有千絲萬縷關係<br />\n以前成日飛上去開會 甚至協助國家改革同經營<br />\n大半年前睇過佢專訪<br />\n<br />\n香港本土店太少分佈 有無得拆"},{"pid":"bdf377f8b24630df424f1f2ca9f06b896b19dddc","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"美心當然不是無辜，重奪經濟救港，由幫襯黃色小店做起！"},{"pid":"777e90426b5908e69f99a43de1c265754aa75c4b","tid":1617433,"uid":303932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:10:25.000Z","msg":"退而求其次，有時真係唔知藍黃，都應該幫襯小店先。大集團係藍嘅機率比較高，唯一肯定例外就係一路都用杜汶澤代言嘅大快活"},{"pid":"96ee18d381dc79c2e861e1566a027d